        "timestamp": "2019-03-28 13:22:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nSystemd in container is not working, if i'm doing something wrong please advise:\n\n$ docker exec -it 4d6f2651b011 systemctl status\nFailed to get D-Bus connection: Operation not permitted",
